	(10, 'SwiftSync Precision Wireless Mouse.', 'swiftsync-precision-wireless-mouse', 'WM2303M', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 'SwiftSync Precision Wireless Mouse, a technological marvel that redefines the way you navigate your digital world. Seamlessly blending precision.', '<p><b>Wireless Freedom:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Break free from the constraints of cables and enjoy the freedom to move with the SwiftSync Precision Wireless Mouse. Its advanced wireless technology ensures a stable and responsive connection, allowing you to work or game with ease from anywhere in the room.</span><br></p><p><b>Precision Tracking:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Navigate with confidence using the SwiftSyncs precision tracking technology. Whether youre editing documents, designing graphics, or gaming, experience smooth and accurate cursor control for enhanced productivity and performance.</span><br></p><p><b>Ergonomic Comfort:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Designed with your comfort in mind, the SwiftSync Precision Wireless Mouse features an ergonomic shape that fits naturally in your hand. Say goodbye to discomfort during long hours of use and hello to a mouse that supports your hands natural contours.</span><br></p><p><b>Effortless Scrolling:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Effortlessly scroll through web pages, documents, and spreadsheets with the SwiftSyncs responsive scroll wheel. The tactile feedback ensures a satisfying and intuitive scrolling experience for efficient navigation.</span><br></p><p><b>Customizable Buttons:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Tailor the mouse to your preferences with customizable buttons. Assign frequently used functions to the programmable buttons for quick access, streamlining your workflow and giving you</span><br></p>', 7, '8-1702303074.jpg', 1, 2, '20', 2, 100, 500.00, 550.00, 200.00, '2024-01-26 12:13:00', '2027-12-31 17:59:00', 1, NULL, '2024-01-22 01:05:00', '2024-01-22 01:05:00'),
	(11, 'Tyota Horizon X: Elevate.', 'tyota-horizon-x-elevate', 'Tyc2023A', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 'Tyota Horizon X -This exceptional car seamlessly blends cutting-edge technology, unparalleled performance, and sophisticated design, offering a driving experience like no other.', '<p><b>Key Features:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;"><b>Dynamic Performance:</b> The Tyota Horizon X is engineered for exhilarating performance, powered by a state-of-the-art engine that delivers a perfect balance of power and fuel efficiency. Whether navigating city streets or cruising on the open highway, experience driving at its finest.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;"><b>Smart Connectivity:</b> Stay seamlessly connected with the intuitive infotainment system. The Tyota Horizon X features advanced connectivity options, including Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, ensuring that you can access your favorite apps, music, and navigation with ease.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;"><b>Safety Redefined:</b> Tyota prioritizes your safety with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features. From adaptive cruise control to lane departure warning, the Horizon X is equipped to keep you and your passengers safe on every journey.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;"><b>Luxurious Interior:</b> Step inside the cabin, where comfort meets elegance. The Tyota Horizon X boasts a meticulously designed interior with premium materials, ergonomic seating, and thoughtful details that elevate your driving experience.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;"><b>Sleek Exterior Design</b>: Make a statement on the road with the Tyota Horizon Xs sleek and aerodynamic exterior. The modern design, stylish contours, and signature Tyota grille combine to create a car that turns heads wherever you go.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;"><b>Efficiency at Its Core: </b>Embrace eco-friendly driving without compromising performance. The Tyota Horizon X incorporat