	(14, 'Stand Table To Set Accesorries.', 'stand-table-to-set-accesorries', 'ST2033A', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 'The Radiance Broom isnt just a cleaning tool; its a household hero. Crafted with precision bristles and an ergonomic handle, it effortlessly sweeps away dirt, leaving your floors gleaming.', '<p><b>Effortless Cleaning with Radiance Broom:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">The Radiance Broom isnt just a cleaning tool; its a household hero. Crafted with precision bristles and an ergonomic handle, it effortlessly sweeps away dirt, leaving your floors gleaming. Embrace the joy of efficient cleaning with this essential household companion.</span><br></p><p><b>Culinary Mastery with CulinaChef Knife Set:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Unleash your inner chef with the CulinaChef Knife Set. Precision-engineered blades meet ergonomic handles for a perfect balance of form and function. Elevate your culinary creations and make every meal preparation a work of art.</span><br></p><p><b>Laundry Bliss with FreshGlow Fabric Softener:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Transform your laundry routine with FreshGlow Fabric Softener. Indulge in the luxurious softness it brings to your clothes while enjoying the invigorating fragrance that lingers. Rediscover the joy of wearing garments that feel as good as they look.</span><br></p><p><b>Smart Storage with SpaceSaver Organizers:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Tame the clutter and reclaim your space with SpaceSaver Organizers. These sleek, stackable wonders maximize storage efficiency, turning chaotic spaces into organized sanctuaries. Experience the liberation of a tidy home without compromising on style.</span><br></p><p><b>Revolutionize Cleaning with PureMist Cleaning Spray:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Introducing PureMist Cleaning Spray, a game-changer in household cleaning. This eco-friendly powerhouse effortlessly tackles grime and germs, leaving surfaces sparkling clean and your home smelling fresh. Embrace the future of clean with this essential addition to your cleaning arsenal.</span><br></p><p><b>Tranquil Ambiance with ZenAura Oil Diffuser:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Transform your living space into a haven of tranquility with the ZenAura Oil Diffuser. Elegant design meets therapeutic functionality, providing a soothing ambiance with your favorite essential oils. Elevate your home environment with this serene addition.</span><br></p>', 4, '2-1702312154.jpg', 1, 1, '200', 2, 1, 1500.00, 2000.00, 700.00, '2025-12-30 00:00:00', '2027-12-31 17:59:00', 1, NULL, '2024-01-22 01:05:00', '2024-01-22 01:05:00');
