	(16, 5, 'code-editor', '39b6e9e', '{"content":"<p>Comprehensive terms and conditions for an auction and bidding of a product are essential to protect both the platform and its users. Below you can use it as a starting point. Keep in mind that its crucial to consult with legal professionals to ensure that these terms comply with local laws and regulations.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><b>BidOut-&nbsp;Auction and Bidding <\\/b>Platform Terms and Conditions<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\">1. Acceptance of Terms<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-size: 1rem;\\">By accessing and using [Your Website Name] (hereinafter referred to as \\"the Website\\"), you agree to comply with and be bound by these terms and conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you must not use the Website.<\\/span><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\">2. User Accounts<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-size: 1rem;\\"><b>2.1.<\\/b> To access certain features of the Website, you may need to create a user account. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account information and agree to accept responsibility for all activities that occur under your account.<\\/span><br><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-size: 1rem;\\"><b>2.2.<\\/b> You must provide accurate and complete information when creating your account. If you provide any information that is untrue, inaccurate, not current, or incomplete, we reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account.<\\/span><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><b>3. Auctions and Bidding Process<\\/b><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-size: 1rem;\\"><b>3.1.<\\/b> The Website acts as a platform for users to participate in auctions and place bids on items. The highest bid at the end of the auction period will be deemed the winner.<\\/span><br><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-size: 1rem;\\"><b>3.2.<\\/b> All bids placed are final and cannot be retracted. By placing a bid, you are committing to